i## Modifying the configuration file		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
iThe nginx configuration also needs modification to enable TLS 1.3. In		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
ithe server block of nginx.conf:		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i1. Modify `ssl_protocols` to add `TLSv1.3`		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i2. Modify `ssl_ciphers` , adding at the beginning:		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i   `TLS13-AES-256-GCM-SHA384:TLS13-CHACHA20-POLY1305-SHA256:TLS13-AES-		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i   128-GCM-SHA256:TLS13-AES-128-CCM-8-SHA256:TLS13-AES-128-CCM-SHA256`		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
iExample after modification:		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i  ssl_protocols TLSv1 TLSv1.1 TLSv1.2 TLSv1.3;		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i  ssl_ciphers 'TLS13-AES-256-GCM-SHA384:TLS13-CHACHA20-POLY1305-SHA256:TLS13-AES-128-GCM-SHA256:TLS13-AES-128-CCM-8-SHA256:TLS13-AES-128-CCM-SHA256:ECDHE-ECDSA-CHACHA20-POLY1305:ECDHE-RSA-CHACHA20-POLY1305:ECDHE-ECDSA-AES128-GCM-SHA256:ECDHE-RSA-AES128-GCM-SHA256:ECDHE-ECDSA-AES256-GCM-SHA384:ECDHE-RSA-AES256-GCM-SHA384:DHE-RSA-AES128-GCM-SHA256:DHE-RSA-AES256-GCM-SHA384:ECDHE-ECDSA-AES128-SHA256:ECDHE-RSA-AES128-SHA256:ECDHE-ECDSA-AES128-SHA:ECDHE-RSA-AES256-SHA384:ECDHE-RSA-AES128-SHA:ECDHE-ECDSA-AES256-SHA384:ECDHE-ECDSA-AES256-SHA:ECDHE-RSA-AES256-SHA:DHE-RSA-AES128-SHA256:DHE-RSA-AES128-SHA:DHE-RSA-AES256-SHA256:DHE-RSA-AES256-SHA:ECDHE-ECDSA-DES-CBC3-SHA:ECDHE-RSA-DES-CBC3-SHA:EDH-RSA-DES-CBC3-SHA:AES128-GCM-SHA256:AES256-GCM-SHA384:AES128-SHA256:AES256-SHA256:AES128-SHA:AES256-SHA:DES-CBC3-SHA:!DSS';		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
